org.lightsleep.entity

Annotation Type Key


  • @Documented
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=FIELD)
public @interface Key
    Indicates that the column associated with the field is part of the primary key.
    Example of use
     public class Phone {
   @Keypublic int contactId;
   @Keypublic short childIndex;
    SQL
     UPDATE Phone ... WHERE contactId=100 AND childIndex=0
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Masato Kokubo
    See Also:
    KeyProperty, KeyProperties
